      "layout": "The page primarily uses a full-bleed pattern for its background colors (Canvas White), but content within these sections is constrained to a central max-width viewport (implicitly present, though not explicitly defined by a max-width token). The hero section features a large, centered headline over a dark background section, establishing a strong typographic focal point. Sections are clearly delineated by generous vertical spacing (`100px` to `108px`) and sometimes by subtle background color changes (e.g., `#f2f2f2` to a darker block). Content arrangement frequently uses a text-left, image-right or vice-versa alternating pattern, and showcases work in a clean grid-like structure (e.g., 2-column image grid). The navigation is a minimalist top bar, likely sticky, with spaced-out text links.",
